label: Legal Daily
title: Legal_Daily
exrest: Legal Daily is a People's Republic of China state-owned newspaper under the supervision of the CCP's Central Commission for Political and Legal Affairs that is published in the PRC and primarily covers legal developments, such as important court rulings. Before 2001, Legal Daily was an organ of the Ministry of Justice.
